g src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DxpCIFgVAAAn6Lu.jpg:large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDxpCIFgVAAAn6Lu.jpg%3Alarge&h=e6ccb3ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/51155451_2167817329905889_6043367530658004992_n.jpg?_nc_cat=108&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=12e54b8d5681f4757052745623c398fd&amp;oe=5CFD1D33\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F51155451_2167817329905889_6043367530658004992_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D108%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3D12e54b8d5681f4757052745623c398fd%26oe%3D5CFD1D33&h=8ec3cbdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSheryl Sanchez Reyes係菲律賓好出名既經紀人<br />\nMighty Sports除咗有奧當，<br />\n仲有18年ABL冠軍火焰隊功臣Justin Brownlee<br />\n同埋Randolph Morris，都係跟呢個女人<br />\n已經有新聞開始炒作奧當會唔會打ABL<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而呢個女人今年就帶左Ramos打ABL火焰<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DxnqWX6UcAAJFcH.jpg:large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDxnqWX6UcAAJFcH.jpg%3Alarge&h=327d3757&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b599436c66d656f85e9c6203f9d4e28af87f2d4a","tid":994902,"uid":106189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T13:46:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UsnC-YPXR6s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUsnC-YPXR6s&d=9P9Iq%2B49TWHZ5%2Bjigqrf1kbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=8497c331\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UsnC-YPXR6s</a><br />\n<br />\n栃木今年有比江島慎回歸"}]}